Yes it's more compact! but it would be better to check if the slackTerminal is cleanable only if required, so:
default SlackTerminal setTerminal(Terminal terminal, boolean cleanIfCleanable) {
    setTerminal(terminal);
    if (cleanIfCleanable && isCleanable()) {
        getExtendable().removeExtension(SlackTerminal.class);
    }
    return this;
}

